# Coding Conventions

## Formatting (verifiable)
- Indentation: {{INDENT}} (e.g. "Use 2-space indentation").
- Formatter: run `{{FORMAT_CMD}}` before committing.
- Linter: `{{LINT_CMD}}` must pass.

## Naming
- Files: {{FILE_NAMING}}.
- Variables/functions: {{VAR_NAMING}}.
- Constants: {{CONST_NAMING}}.

## File structure
- A file is at most ~{{MAX_FILE_LINES}} lines; split if it exceeds.
- Import order: {{IMPORT_ORDER}}.

## General rules
- No dead code / unused imports.
- Comments must match the existing codebase's language.
